timeStamps.text: In 1985 Mexico City, Heinrich Treadway tries to escape the authorities and a man
He and his associates, Abel and Leona speak about "the Egg
Treadway tells Abel that if he does not survive
the latter must remember to "look inside"
He drives off a bridge, jumping from his car in mid-air and onto another bridge 150 feet away.
However, Treadway watches helplessly as Bathurst arrives and kills Abel and Leona.
